{"tid":140314,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得邊隊\"Golden team\"贏唔到冠軍(球會/國家隊)係好可惜既事?","createTime":"2017-03-02T05:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T04:21:22.000Z","uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd5cac3f01219f92a208be2c508a06ea97d0c47","tid":140314,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"golden team=粒粒皆星, 仲要有實力(唔係得個樣)<br />\n<br />\n1954, 匈牙利既Golden Team, 當時粒粒皆星, 有Pusk&aacute;s, 決賽時比德國黑哨贏左<br />\n1974, 荷蘭全能足球, 仲有荷蘭球王告魯夫, 決賽比碧根鮑華既德國擊敗<br />\n2006, now or never既有今生無來世既球隊, 前中後場粒粒皆星, 實力頂級既英格蘭, 因為肥仔既魯網, 害到英格蘭打小1個, 12碼互射出局<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e26031b9a5b21cdc2305edf7dd330ed525e4b21","tid":140314,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:55:08.000Z","msg":"伊度亞度年代阿狗"},{"pid":"0582107c7903c157f4c74036b0b500dd2bf584be","tid":140314,"uid":42375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:58:23.000Z","msg":"川崎前鋒"},{"pid":"70a1e0dadb8d11a303543715cb3939052cfcd493","tid":140314,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"1954, 1974年的人, 我只係聽過下<br />\n但2006年英格蘭, 真係好令人心傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n碧咸, 肥仔, 雙特, terry, Ferdinand, 卡域克, a cole<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果肥仔害芥蘭打小一個, 一早贏左冠軍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd2c8461fe03db89dd400d7df6abf841d89febf","tid":140314,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"2006既巴西"},{"pid":"f47c906013c4969f50494a5564d7eb25a9fca573","tid":140314,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2006既巴西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢隊人腳就勁, 但得個樣, 踼出效果唔太好<br />\n而且其實當時巴西球員之間有內閧, 唔團結<br />\n<br />\n1990年荷蘭三劍俠時代, 都係人強馬壯, 但又係黑白人內閧, 唔團結, 打得好差"},{"pid":"b2e9d40548bcb31dbaee4102b302bcfdcdef69b0","tid":140314,"uid":135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:05:57.000Z","msg":"02 意大利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母死韓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe8825c55ed9605c910c9650b85e42892eeb75a","tid":140314,"uid":15724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:10:19.000Z","msg":"Ac米蘭 2005年 講真當年人腳真係ac近20年最勁 前中後都屈機 決賽半場都3:0 下半場真係輸果6分鐘 輸埋個勢  猁反cup係幾勁 但我肯定米蘭半場3:0果時已經輕晒敵 放鬆左 <br />\n就算07復仇番 但07年猁人腳其實比米蘭勁 米蘭人腳老化 只係卡卡一個太屈 就整體 05果隊最勁但冇冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed4ccd4f143bee4d6ec540e5bab50723aff6cf8","tid":140314,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2006既巴西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢隊人腳就勁, 但得個樣, 踼出效果唔太好</span><br />\n而且其實當時巴西球員之間有內閧, 唔團結<br />\n<br />\n1990年荷蘭三劍俠時代, 都係人強馬壯, 但又係黑白人內閧, 唔團結, 打得好差</blockquote><br />\n06英格蘭咪一樣？得個樣最後都係要靠碧咸"},{"pid":"133bba42d4b7577f1a0adc583c336621985f46d1","tid":140314,"uid":30773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:20:03.000Z","msg":"06英撚真係黃金一代"},{"pid":"55f33523a102749f7ed84cee5122f4d7871e262d","tid":140314,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"2014 利記"},{"pid":"fb77c03cb0c3404dfa87b104d63a661787943b31","tid":140314,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>02 意大利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母死韓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></block